ethemoglobin-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/145229/', '', 'Tinidazole, Linezolid, Bacitracin, Oritavancin, Polymyxin B, Daptomycin, Vancomycin, Metronidazole, Telavancin, Methenamine, Spectinomycin, More', '', 1767369485);
